T*
(- Stoichiometry should first be understood as a chemical idea before it is treated as an) Tj
T*
(exam topic.) Tj
T*
(- The learner must understand mole ratios and converting between quantities because it) Tj
T*
(controls how questions in Stoichiometry are answered correctly.) Tj
T*
(- A strong answer in Stoichiometry uses the correct chemical reasoning process and) Tj
T*
(explains why that method fits the task.) Tj
